ing: 2 medium papayas, cut in half lengthwise and seeded
des: "Papayas stuffed with yogurt, raisins, strawberries, and walnuts are topped with honey. Choose ripe papayas with reddish-brown skin that is soft to the touch; avoid green papayas, as they are not yet ripe. Organic ingredients taste best!"
ins: In a bowl, mix the yogurt, walnuts, and raisins. Fold in the strawberries. Spoon the mixture into the centers of the papaya halves. Drizzle with honey to serve.
